on of Classmate |publisher=TIME |date= |accessdate=2014-07-31 |archive-date=2014-07-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140731003036/http://time.com/3048633/japanese-schoolgirl-arrested-for-murdering-dismembering-classmate/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="japantimes1">{{cite web |url=http://www.japantimes.co.jp/news/2014/07/31/national/crime-legal/after-grisly-sasebo-killing-teachers-community-wonder-if-there-were-signs/ |title=Sasebo searches for missed signals |publisher=The Japan Times |date= |accessdate=2014-07-31 |archive-date=2014-08-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140802201032/http://www.japantimes.co.jp/news/2014/07/31/national/crime-legal/after-grisly-sasebo-killing-teachers-community-wonder-if-there-were-signs/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.japantimes.co.jp/news/2014/08/01/national/crime-legal/psychiatrist-warned-officials-june-sasebo-girl-may-commit-murder/ |title=Psychiatrist warned officials in June that Sasebo girl may commit murder |publisher=The Japan Times |date=2014-08-01 |accessdate=2014-08-01 |archive-date=2014-08-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140802184731/http://www.japantimes.co.jp/news/2014/08/01/national/crime-legal/psychiatrist-warned-officials-june-sasebo-girl-may-commit-murder/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://mainichi.jp/english/english/newsselect/news/20140801p2g00m0dm028000c.html |title=Welfare center received warning in June about teen held for murder - 毎日新聞 |publisher=Mainichi.jp |date=2014-08-01 |accessdate=2014-08-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140808053002/http://mainichi.jp/english/english/newsselect/news/20140801p2g00m0dm028000c.html |archivedate=2014-08-08 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.japantimes.co.jp/news/2015/01/31/national/media-national/changing-motives-behind-juvenile-crime-japan/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-04-09 |archive-date=2015-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150407234200/http://www.jap